   284â†’			/\b(polo|hoodie|jacket|hat|cap|bag|mug|pen|notebook|shirt|pants|shorts|socks|shoes|sneakers|sweatshirt|fleece|vest|beanie|gloves|scarf|backpack|tote|water bottle|tumbler|keychain|lanyard|umbrella|polo shirt|t-shirt|tank top|zip-up|half-zip|long-sleeve|short-sleeve|crewneck|v-neck)\b/i;
